{"tid":1242720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭絕對不可以落台","createTime":"2019-06-19T07:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:33:07.000Z","uid":42751,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a54f5db3b7b99455dab21f3e0332a2b46c0b197d","tid":1242720,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"林鄭繼續完成如下任期，先至係對香港人最大保障：<br />\n<br />\n1. 林鄭已經成為跛腳鴨政府， 餘下任期再有任何嚴重出賣港人利益嘅政策， 例如23條， 以林鄭嘅民望一定冇可能通過， 香港人反而可以安穩度過未來三年。如果北京再搵一個好似梁振英咁奸嘅人接手特首， 我哋又要由頭嚟過有排驚<br />\n<br />\n2. 林鄭自視過高、目中無人、唔聽其他人講， 呢一種性格對香港市民嚟講反而係最大嘅優點， 只要佢繼續唔認輸， 隨時可以再一次火燒北京後欄， 為美國貿易戰同埋台獨勢力無限供應子彈， 日日搞習近平後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林太我支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfa70fcdc8631652e9701026469b46a683880c4","tid":1242720,"uid":258598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6c73822b727df38ed03e458fc68f2c5e1367e9d","tid":1242720,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"的確 佢依家咁弱勢 仲點推其他爭議法案 例如23條, 留個虛君喺度仲好"},{"pid":"81329b9a2f968a09457f8c214f0921784d873bd7","tid":1242720,"uid":216433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"港獨之母"},{"pid":"7b258b68cbc41d9aadc51303d60919c096f029ba","tid":1242720,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6c73822b727df38ed03e458fc68f2c5e1367e9d","tid":1242720,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T07:56:46.000Z","msg":"的確 佢依家咁弱勢 仲點推其他爭議法案 例如23條, 留個虛君喺度仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-